iMonday is Bun Day here in Iceland. Bollur, the buns of the day,		gopher.black	70
iare sort of like cream puffs. Folks get jams and whipped cream and		gopher.black	70
imix them together and stuff the buns to overflowing, then smother		gopher.black	70
ithem in chocolate sauce. It's a healthy time!		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iThere's also a super-duper Icelandic tradition with bun day that		gopher.black	70
imany parents choose to not teach their kids. Early on Monday		gopher.black	70
imorning children in the know will wake up early, sneak into their		gopher.black	70
iparents' bedroom and WHACK WHACK WHACK them in their bed with		gopher.black	70
isticks! However many whacks they get in before the parents get up		gopher.black	70
iis how many buns they get. Lovely!		gopher.black	70
