iFinally we get to Ash Wednesday. Here in Iceland Ash Wednesday is		gopher.black	70
ithe costume & candy holiday. Halloween is a relatively recent		gopher.black	70
iphenomenon here and not very popular mostly because they already		gopher.black	70
ihave most of those traditions at the start of lent. Kids dress up		gopher.black	70
iin all sorts of costumes, go to school that way, and then later go		gopher.black	70
iaround begging for candy. But here they don't go to individual		gopher.black	70
ihomes and say "trick or treat". Instead they go to businesses and		gopher.black	70
